{
  "stem": "543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was never-- I never would have picked up that I was-- that they would say, oh, she is like a Muselmann, they called it-- so skinny.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Though they said-- they never would take me for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, even whenever-- when my sister-in-law weighed at the end of the war 64 pounds, I weighed 125.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I-- when I came-- later, when I came out of the war and I went to-- by my doctors, they used to say, look what happened to the ladies-- went through the same thing, the same food.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked-- you know, they never-- I looked good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I-- that was one of things that saved me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the other thing was that-- I told you Lillian was very good looking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was blonde.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the SS always thought she was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they always used to say, you're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so an SS saw her walking with-- and he took her out of the row and said, you're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, yes, I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was always with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was afraid that she would be separated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she asked-- she said, that is my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used to say I don't want to go away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said that is-- then they said, but you don't look alike.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, she said that is my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she looks like my mother or opposite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what they say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she did not want to get a special treatment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was-- she was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- so we stayed always together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we one time, we were in a commando-- like we get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
